tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE inventory (
    product_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (product_id, timestamp)
);

CREATE TABLE sales_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    item_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    revenue DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE sales_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    sale_amount INT,
    sale_date DATE,
    store_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE inventory (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INTEGER,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE sales (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INTEGER,
    quantity_sold INTEGER,
    profit DECIMAL(10, 2),
    sale_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE suppliers (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    order_date DATE,
    product_id INTEGER,
    quantity_ordered INTEGER,
    customer_id INTEGER
);
